{"tid":1122823,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完end game嘅入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-04-24T06:50:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T15:48:16.000Z","uid":211270,"like":3,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"bb15fd565361dc5f585649aa06828fd42fada673","tid":1122823,"uid":211270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T06:50:36.000Z","msg":"其實marvel係咪玩亂左條timeline?<br />\n<br />\n首先，根據ancient one同hulk嘅對話，可以知道所有人都活喺同一條timeline上面，因為佢地最後有還返d石去原位，防止分支出現。<br />\n<br />\n照呢個邏輯，改變過去會直接影響現在同未來：<br />\n1. Nabula殺左過去嘅自己，咁係咪有bugs? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.過去(2014)嚟嘅Thanos化左灰，咁即係infinity war唔會發生?<br />\n3.Thor係過去攞左個槌，咁過去嘅Thor咪唔見左個槌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(除非佢之後返去還返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n主要bugs就諗到呢3個<br />\n<br />\n如果改變過去會產生分支(平行宇宙)，咁成件事就冇意思，因為佢地只係拯救到自己個宇宙，喺其他分支依然係Thanos最後成功。所以個設定唔會係咁樣。<br />\n<br />\n另外，其實time travel之後，復仇者先係令thanos可以集齊6粒石嘅元凶? 因為thanos見到未來nabula嘅記憶先知道6粒石嘅位置。<br />\n<br />\n有冇人解釋到個bugs? 如有錯請指證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4c4084e619caf634010dae0a4853694fba74e21","tid":1122823,"uid":211270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T07:53:16.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6642374c4d440e4c2630c4b51d04aaa4b3b173a","tid":1122823,"uid":211270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T07:56:12.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ab3270427eeb254efa8ae769722b455865a75d","tid":1122823,"uid":211270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T07:59:25.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a586c5210ead41453343838eb3beb39943fcc269","tid":1122823,"uid":3860,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T08:03: